  "response": "Finding a good laptop under \u20b935,000 in India can be challenging, but there are several decent options available that offer good value for money. Here are some recommendations based on your budget:\n\n---\n\n### **1. HP 15s (2023)**  \n- **Processor**: Intel Core i3-1115G4  \n- **RAM**: 8GB DDR4  \n- **Storage**: 512GB SSD  \n- **Display**: 15.6-inch FHD (1920x1080)  \n- **OS**: Windows 11 Home  \n- **Price**: ~\u20b934,000 (Amazon/Flipkart)  \n**Pros**: Good battery life, lightweight, SSD for faster performance.  \n\n---\n\n### **2. Lenovo IdeaPad Slim 3 (Intel)**  \n- **Processor**: Intel Core i3-1115G4  \n- **RAM**: 8GB DDR4  \n- **Storage**: 256GB SSD  \n- **Display**: 15.6-inch HD (1366x768)  \n- **OS**: Windows 11 Home  \n- **Price**: ~\u20b933,000 (Amazon/Flipkart)  \n**Pros**: Affordable, reliable performance, Lenovo build quality.  \n\n---\n\n### **3. Acer Aspire Lite (2023)**  \n- **Processor**: Intel Core i3-1115G4  \n- **RAM**: 8GB DDR4  \n- **Storage**: 512GB SSD  \n- **Display**: 15.6-inch FHD (1920x1080)  \n- **OS**: Windows 11 Home  \n- **Price**: ~\u20b934,000 (Amazon/Flipkart)  \n**Pros**: Sleek design, good performance for the price, SSD storage.  \n\n---\n\n### **4. Dell Inspiron 3520**  \n- **Processor**: Intel Core i3-1215U  \n- **RAM**: 8GB DDR4  \n- **Storage**: 256GB SSD  \n- **Display**: 15.6-inch FHD (1920x1080)  \n- **OS**: Windows 11 Home  \n- **Price**: ~\u20b935,000 (Amazon/Flipkart)  \n**Pros**: Reliable build, latest processor, Dell support.  \n\n---\n\n### **5. ASUS VivoBook 15**  \n- **Processor**: Intel Core i3-1115G4  \n- **RAM**: 8GB DDR4  \n- **Storage**: 256GB SSD  \n- **Display**: 15.6-inch HD (1366x768)  \n- **OS**: Windows 11 Home  \n- **Price**: ~\u20b934,000 (Amazon/Flipkart)  \n**Pros**: Slim and lightweight, good for daily use.  \n\n---\n\n### **Key Things to Consider**  \n- **Processor**: Look for at least an Intel i3 or AMD Ryzen 3.  \n- **RAM**: 8GB is ideal for multitasking.  \n- **Storage**: SSD 